### HELLO, WROLD!

Welcome to the *Intermediate JavaScript Workshop*! Today we will programming concepts and topics in javascript that will teach you how to write clean, reusable code. 

#### In a nutshell

These are our three main objectives for today:

1. Learn about the functional fundamentals of JavaScript.
2. Learn about object oriented fundamentals of JavaScript.
3. Learn about popular design patterns used in writing JS code.

